trans-unit.source: Represents the child controls of containers that support <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer underordnede kontroller over beholdere som støtter <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This control pattern is analogous to <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern> with the distinction that any control supporting TableItemPattern will programmatically expose the relationship between the individual cell and its row and column information.
trans-unit.target: Denne kontrollen mønsteret tilsvarer <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern>med forskjellen noen kontrollere støttet TableItemPattern vil programmatisk vise forholdet mellom individuelle cellen og rad- og informasjonen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern>

trans-unit.source: Access to individual cell functionality is provided by the additional support of <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern>.
trans-unit.target: Tilgang til enkelte celler funksjonene leveres av ytterligere støtte for <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern>

trans-unit.source: Gets the cached property values for this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter bufrede egenskapsverdiene for denne <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Cached property values must have been previously requested using a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.
trans-unit.target: Bufret egenskapsverdier må tidligere er forespurt ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>

trans-unit.source: To get the current value of a property, get the property by using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: For å hente gjeldende verdi for en egenskap, kan du hente egenskapen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Current%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: For information on the properties available and their use, see <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om egenskapene som er tilgjengelige og bruken, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>

trans-unit.source: The cached property values.
trans-unit.target: De hurtigbufrede egenskapsverdiene.

trans-unit.source: The requested property is not in the cache.
trans-unit.target: Den forespurte egenskapen er ikke i hurtigbufferen.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the property that retrieves all the column headers associated with a table item or cell.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer egenskapen som henter alle kolonneoverskrifter som er knyttet til et tabellelement eller en celle.

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation client applications.
trans-unit.target: Denne identifikatoren brukes av Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation providers should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPatternIdentifiers>.
trans-unit.target: Brukergrensesnittet Automation leverandører må bruke det tilsvarende feltet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPatternIdentifiers>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPatternIdentifiers>

trans-unit.source: This property is not present in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation> and must be retrieved by using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen finnes ikke i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>og må hentes ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>

trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current property values for this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter gjeldende egenskapsverdiene for denne <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This pattern must be from an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> with an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> reference in order to get current values.
trans-unit.target: Dette mønsteret må være fra en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>med en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>referanse for å hente gjeldende verdier.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> was obtained using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, it contains only cached data, and attempting to get the current value of any property raises an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>ble hentet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, den inneholder bare bufrede data, og forsøk på å hente gjeldende verdi for en egenskap viser et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Cached%2A> to get the cached value of a property that was previously specified using a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Cached%2A>hente bufrede verdien for en egenskap som ble tidligere definert ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.Cached%2A>

trans-unit.source: For information on the properties available and their use, see <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om egenskapene som er tilgjengelige og bruken, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern.TableItemPatternInformation>
